{"data":[{"date":"09:48 15/07","title":"Mourinho g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u1edbn khi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/mourinho-gap-kho-khan-lon-khi-chuan-bi-truoc-mua-giai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i, nh\u01b0ng HLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 World Cup, khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang M\u1ef9, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1 gi\u1ea3i ICC v\u00e0 t\u00edch l\u0169y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 &ldquo;pre-season&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u01a1n 10 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, v\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 (c\u1ee7a Anh, Ph\u00e1p, B\u1ec9) chinh chi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho Premier League ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y&rdquo; &ndash; Jose Mourinho t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, &ldquo;b\u1edfi v\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n \u0111ang \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga. \u0110\u00f3 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y \u0111i c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\" title=\"Pogba vs Fellaini\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Paul-Pogba-phat-bieu-ve-DT-Phap-va-ban-than-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y \u0111i c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;3 tu\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, tinh th\u1ea7n, \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 quay l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. \u0110\u01b0a h\u1ecd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u01b0? OK th\u00f4i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t h\u1ecd v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong 3-4 th\u00e1ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 3 tu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ngay trong tu\u1ea7n Premier League khai m\u1ea1c, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u, khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7&rdquo; &ndash; Mourinho ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 World Cup.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 5/8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Bayern Munich. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t chia s\u1ebb, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1ef1 d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t. \u1ede k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp theo, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00f2n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, khi n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qatar s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup 2022 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester-172-191192.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester-172-191192.html\">Th\u00eam b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y M.U s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Manchester \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 M.U.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/roy-keane-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-dt-anh-421-191201.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/roy-keane-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-dt-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/roy-keane-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-dt-anh-421-191201.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e9p v\u1ebf v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng Ba tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U Roy Keane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1279","checkdouble":"191232"},{"date":"10:04 15/07","title":"Real Madrid h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Mateo Kovacic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/2/real-madrid-het-gia-khong-tuong-cho-mateo-kovacic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid b\u00e1n Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kovacic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Modric v\u00e0 Kroos. Los Blancos v\u1eeba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Modric \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid b\u00e1n Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid b\u00e1n Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/real-madrid-het-gia-khong-tuong-cho-mateo-kovacic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh quan t\u00e2m Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 Kovacic nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin Kovacic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u1ede Anh, c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i, bao g\u1ed3m MU, Man City v\u00e0 Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-sao-real-madrid-172-189650.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU nh\u1eafm Kovacic thay th\u1ebf Carrick</span>, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7. Tottenham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia thay th\u1ebf cho Dembele, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City \u0111ang th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf so v\u1edbi Chelsea \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Jorginho, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994. Man xanh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau\u00a0m\u1ed9 c\u1ef1u sao Inter Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real \u0111\u00f2i 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid b\u00e1n Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Daily Star kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Los Blancos \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real vs PSG Kovacic\" title=\"Real vs PSG Kovacic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/7/mu-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-sao-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua Kovacic t\u1eeb Inter Milan, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. D\u00f9 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i, song h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Real h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, Kovacic s\u1ebd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0 \u1edf c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng xong. N\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Modric v\u00e0 Kroos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1278","checkdouble":"191234"},{"date":"10:21 15/07","title":"Man City tr\u00e1ch Lukaku l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a De Bruyne","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/man-city-trach-lukaku-lang-phi-tai-nang-cua-de-bruyne.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i hay \u1edf l\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Bale b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Bale b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh r\u1ea5t vui khi CR7 ra \u0111i, b\u1edfi khi \u0111\u00f3 Bale s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Lopetegui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Lopetegui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/chot-thoi-diem-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Gareth Bale\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bale s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh khi m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Donbalon th\u00ec l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng Bale \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Lopetegui c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Isco v\u00e0 Asensio, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng n\u00e0y tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN v\u00e0 gh\u1ebb l\u1ea1nh Bale l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Real \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Gareth Bale lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i hay \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"guong mat phan cam Gareth Bale\" title=\"guong mat phan cam Gareth Bale\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bale s\u1ebd b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n n\u1ebfu Lopetegui t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Daily Mail, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Bale l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real, n\u1ebfu m\u1ea5t th\u00eam Bale tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u1ecb x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/real-giam-gia-ban-gareth-bale-cho-mu-172-184790.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Bale</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tottenham v\u00e0 Bayern Munich c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1277","checkdouble":"191235"},{"date":"10:10 15/07","title":"Kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Hazard, tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Chelsea tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u1edf l\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>K\u1ebft th\u00fac World Cup 2018, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Eden Hazard, Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid, anh tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i qua, Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Ngay sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng r\u1eddi CLB Chelsea sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAi c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft Hazard \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ea7m m\u1eaft v\u1ec1 Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi anh trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. Cristiano Ronaldo m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 gia nh\u1eadp, t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hazard tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng l\u00e0 Maurizio Sarri b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Jorginho.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Hazard, Thibaut Courtois c\u0169ng n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, anh cho bi\u1ebft v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois noi ve tuong lai\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i s\u1ebd n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 xem \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea\u201d, t\u1edd Marca tr\u00edch l\u1eddi Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi lu\u00f4n ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u1ecd c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng CLB s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, ngay c\u1ea3 khi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c \u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, b\u1edfi v\u00ec t\u00f4i th\u00edch th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 London.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0 <br>\r\nCourtois \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 n\u0103m 2011 t\u1eeb Genk. Anh tr\u1ea3i qua 3 n\u0103m d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Atletico Madrid v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\">N\u00f3ng: Hazard \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nongs-hazard-sap-co-ben-do-moi-172-191182.html\">N\u00d3NG: Eden Hazard s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-chinh-thuc-bo-nhiem-nguoi-thay-the-conte-172-191167.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Chelsea CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Conte</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1276","checkdouble":"191236"},{"date":"09:54 15/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1: C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/diem-nhan-sau-tran-hagl-31-can-tho-cong-dau-cua-van-toan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hay Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng HAGL, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</h2><h2>1. M\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 HAGL sau pha b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ebfm th\u1ea5y c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng treo b\u00f3ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a V\u0103n S\u01a1n, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o qu\u00ea H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o g\u00f3c xa, \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i T\u00f4 V\u0129nh L\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ecfng, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong 45 ph\u00fat hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/anh3_2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n To\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt ph\u00fat, V\u0103n To\u00e0n l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edb t\u1edbi sau pha d\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng xu\u1ed1ng bi\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhanh b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1\u00a0tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u1ecdn c\u1ed7 v\u00e0o trong cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Osmar l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 3 trong 4 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00f3ng vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng cho HAGL. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh hay tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 2-2 t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1eadp nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u r\u1ea5t vui cho HAGL trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong t\u1ed1p 3 khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n ngo\u1ea1i binh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Osmar Francisco ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho HAGL. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ghi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n cho \u2018G\u1ed7\u2019 tuy nhi\u00ean h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-4 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Osmar ghi b\u00e0n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u0169ng x\u00f3a tan \u0111i nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i SLNA. L\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u00f3c, Osmar nhanh ch\u00f3ng th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i HAGL.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/aGFnbF9jb25ncGh1b25nX2FubXVuZw==.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c ngo\u1ea1i binh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 b\u1eaft nh\u1ecbp nhanh c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u m\u1eebng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai khi m\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Osmar, c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Zeba Josip, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh m\u1edbi n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a HAGL. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, Zeba \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 theo k\u00e8m ch\u00e2n s\u00fat nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, Patiyo. Ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a HAGL th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. \u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a \u2018G\u1ed7\u2019<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 s\u01a1 h\u1edf \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. N\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Pleiku \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 1 khi b\u00f3ng d\u1ed9i v\u00e0o x\u00e0 ngang b\u1eadt ra sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Ho\u00e0ng Vissai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u00ean h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 HAGL v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00fat 61 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ngo\u1ea1i binh Wander Luiz b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb theo k\u00e8m \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft t\u1eeb pha t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. B\u00f3ng \u0111i hi\u1ec3m khi\u1ebfn V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng khi T\u0103ng Tu\u1ea5n lao v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u01a1i cao so v\u1edbi x\u00e0 ngang HAGL. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c khai th\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a HAGL b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec3 Patiyo lao\u00a0v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf trong kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a HAGL. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n th\u00eam k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<h2>4. Th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi b\u1ecb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a t\u1ed1 ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o th\u00eam r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i khi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n x\u00f4 x\u00e1t v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Quang T\u00ecnh b\u00ean ph\u00eda C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 10 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 pha tranh b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau v\u1edbi Quang T\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e0n anh b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch, khi\u1ebfn Quang T\u00ecnh b\u1ecb ng\u00e3. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady, c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o ng\u1ef1c C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 779px;\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width: 777px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width: 777px;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width: 769px;\"><img alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/cp-quangtinh.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HAGL vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat CLB HA Gia Lai c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng v\u1eeba khi \u0111\u1ecbnh lao v\u00e0o tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u0169a, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. R\u1ea5t may sau \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp can ng\u0103n hai c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00f3ng. C\u1ea3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Quang T\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u. \u1ede v\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai b\u1ecb t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o l\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng hay v\u00e0 d\u00f9ng ch\u00e2n t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, b\u1edfi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng n\u1eefa, anh s\u1ebd b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 1 tr\u1eadn. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng.</p>\r\n<h2>5. C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 t\u1ee5t s\u00e2u tr\u00ean BXH<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c TP.HCM b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u00ecm s\u00e2u trong kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 12 tr\u00ean BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. C\u00f3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady h\u1ecd m\u1edbi tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018 sau vong 19\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018 sau v\u00f2ng 19\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/BXH-V-League.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>BXH V-League 2018 sau v\u00f2ng 19</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1275","checkdouble":"191237"},{"date":"10:41 15/07","title":"Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/chot-thoi-diem-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i hay \u1edf l\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Bale b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Bale b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh r\u1ea5t vui khi CR7 ra \u0111i, b\u1edfi khi \u0111\u00f3 Bale s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Lopetegui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Lopetegui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/chot-thoi-diem-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Gareth Bale\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bale s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh khi m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Donbalon th\u00ec l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng Bale \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Lopetegui c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Isco v\u00e0 Asensio, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng n\u00e0y tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN v\u00e0 gh\u1ebb l\u1ea1nh Bale l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Real \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Gareth Bale lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i hay \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"guong mat phan cam Gareth Bale\" title=\"guong mat phan cam Gareth Bale\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bale s\u1ebd b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n n\u1ebfu Lopetegui t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Daily Mail, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Bale l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real, n\u1ebfu m\u1ea5t th\u00eam Bale tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u1ecb x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/real-giam-gia-ban-gareth-bale-cho-mu-172-184790.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Bale</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tottenham v\u00e0 Bayern Munich c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1274","checkdouble":"191238"},{"date":"10:09 15/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh 19h00 ng\u00e0y 15/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/nhan-dinh-ha-noi-vs-nam-dinh-19h00-ngay-157-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 15/7 (V\u00f2ng 19 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh: 2-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nS\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. T\u1eeb l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cho \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng cu\u1ed1i BXH v\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 18 v\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u1ec5m tr\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 47 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a t\u1edbi 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 \u00edt h\u01a1n 1 tr\u1eadn), v\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V.League 2018, ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0o m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u0103ng quang. Do v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thong th\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh g\u00e2y n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 V\u0103n S\u1ef9, gi\u00fap Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\nH\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: V\u0103n C\u00f4ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, V\u0103n Ki\u00ean, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Moses, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ea1i, Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Oseni.<br>\r\nNam \u0110\u1ecbnh: Minh Nh\u1ef1t, Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa, H\u1eefu Qu\u00fd, M\u1ea1nh C\u01b0\u1eddng, Diogo, Henry, \u0110\u1ee9c Nam, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, Qu\u1ed1c H\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, S\u1ef9 Minh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1273","checkdouble":"191239"},{"date":"10:35 15/07","title":"Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Lovren \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-lovren-va-dang-cap-cua-hoc-tro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lovren v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i. HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf Liverpool \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean b\u1ed5 sung r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u00fd ki\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch quan.</h2><h2><br>\r\nLovren \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nDejan Lovren v\u00e0 \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh, n\u01a1i trung v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m trung phong xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc Harry Kane c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i im ti\u1ebfng. Sau tr\u1eadn, Lovren \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ecbp \u201cn\u1ed5 to\u201d khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Lovren tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u1ea3 l\u00e0 su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia s\u1ed1ng trong nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m khi\u1ebfn CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lovren v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lovren v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Lovren-voi-nhung-loi-ca-ngoi-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lovren ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Croatia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKlopp \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nKlopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lovren v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u00d4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng song c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t \u00fd ki\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch quan h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y. \u201cS\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Dejan! Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00f3i \u0111\u00fang\u201d, Klopp n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111i v\u00e0o chi ti\u1ebft, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Croatia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Rakitic, Brozovic, Modric v\u00ec v\u1eady c\u1ea7n ai \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t ph\u00eda sau. Dejan l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u00f3.\u201d <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lovren\" title=\"Lovren\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-lovren-va-dang-cap-cua-hoc-tro.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lovren v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, Klopp c\u0169ng nh\u1eafc kh\u00e9o Lovren c\u1ea7n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u201cDejan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u00e0 3 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 chung k\u1ebft Europa League. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, song v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng nhau trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 HLV Klopp tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-ve-tan-binh-shaqiri-cua-liverpool-172-191149.html\">HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Liverpool?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-daniel-sturridge-172-190783.html\">Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Daniel Sturridge</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/henderson-phat-bieu-ve-klopp-421-190774.html\">Jurgen Klopp \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-mung-ro-voi-man-trinh-dien-cua-2-tan-binh-bom-tan-172-190681.html\">Klopp m\u1eebng r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a 2 t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1272","checkdouble":"191240"},{"date":"11:09 15/07","title":"M\u1edbi t\u1edbi Chelsea, Sarri \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n thanh l\u00fd \u201ct\u00e0n d\u01b0\u201d th\u1eddi Conte","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/20/hlv-sarri-muon-ban-giroud-va-morata.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Giroud v\u00e0 Morata, 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Conte. \u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Napoli mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 tr\u00f2 c\u0169 Higuain t\u1ea1i Chelsea.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ednh t\u1ed1ng kh\u1ee9 Giroud v\u00e0 Morata</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlvaro Morata gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea t\u1eeb Real Madrid m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Morata \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Zinedine Zidane n\u00edu gi\u1eef.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi t\u1edbi Chelsea, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n n\u0103ng \u201cs\u00e1t th\u1ee7\u201d. 48 tr\u1eadn tr\u00f4i qua tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00f9a 2017/18, Morata ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 15 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n n\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Real c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i CLB m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Giroud v\u00e0 Morata, 2 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Giroud v\u00e0 Morata, 2 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/20/hlv-sarri-muon-ban-giroud-va-morata.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Giroud v\u00e0 Morata</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 k\u00e9m duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Morata khi\u1ebfn Chelsea ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Olivier Giroud t\u1eeb Arsenal \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p \u201cch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y\u201d. Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Giroud l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i nh\u01b0ng anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 \u201cb\u1eadt b\u00e3i\u201d kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ea3 l\u00e0 HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Giroud v\u00e0 Morata. T\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ea3 Giroud v\u00e0 Morata \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7u trong khi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Sarri l\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mu\u1ed1n mang v\u1ec1 Higuain</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00eda sau thanh l\u00fd \u201ct\u00e0n d\u01b0\u201d c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Conte, Sarri mu\u1ed1n m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho tr\u00f2 c\u0169 Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi Chelsea. M\u00f9a 2015/16, khi c\u1ea3 hai h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c t\u1ea1i Napoli, Higuain \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 38 b\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 sau 42 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gonzalo Higuain cua Juventus\" title=\"Gonzalo Higuain cua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/23/chelsea-sap-co-tien-dao-tri-gia-53-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea t\u00ednh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Higuain t\u1ea1i Juventus c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t lung lay. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo khi\u1ebfn anh \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh. Th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb Italia cho hay ph\u00eda Juve s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Higuain \u0111\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1edbi Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Sarri l\u1ea1i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea. M\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb 55 t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u Euro l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u00fap The Blues c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Higuain.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 HLV Sarri tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/giai-quyet-xong-conte-chelsea-chuan-bi-don-lien-3-tan-binh-172-191166.html\">Gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft xong Conte, Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n li\u1ec1n 3 t\u00e2n binh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-neu-hlv-sarri-dan-dat-chelsea-thay-conte-172-191110.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1271","checkdouble":"191241"},{"date":"11:39 15/07","title":"Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: 5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/15/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-5-dieu-dang-cho-doi-o-tran-phap-vs-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 22h00 t\u1ed1i nay. V\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u00f3 5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>1. S\u1ef1 tr\u1ed7i d\u1eady c\u1ee7a Mbappe<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 19, Kylian Mbappe \u0111ang l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y CLB PSG \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang khi b\u1ecf ra t\u1edbi 180 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhanh nh\u1eb9n, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 tinh qu\u00e1i, Mbappe \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i e ng\u1ea1i. Anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina, Uruguay v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 5 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 5 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/Chung-ket-World-Cup-2018-5-dieu-cho-doi-o-tran-Phap-vs-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Kylian Mbappe li\u1ec7u s\u1ebd b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n vinh, Mbappe s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c mang t\u00ean Croatia. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y v\u00ec sao h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i, khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh, qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Mbappe nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua, anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng minh cho c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i trong v\u00f3c d\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. Ai s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 Kante nh\u01b0ng Croatia c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu Luka Modric. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ngo\u00e0i tu\u1ed5i b\u0103m song Modric v\u1eabn s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi c\u00f9ng Real chinh ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, Modric \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf gi\u00fap \u0110T Croatia l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric vs Kante\" title=\"Modric vs Kante\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/diem-nhan-2-0950.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Modric v\u00e0 Kante s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn\u00a0Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia s\u1eafp t\u1edbi</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00e2n chuy\u1ec1n Croatia ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1eafp t\u1edbi anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u2018qu\u00e1i th\u00fa\u2019 N\u2019Golo Kante s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 v\u00f4 t\u1eadn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kante t\u1eebng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft Lionel Messi, khi\u1ebfn cho Bentancur v\u00e0 Luis Suarez c\u1ee7a Uruguay hay Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 \u201cm\u1ea5t t\u00edch\u201d. V\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa Kante v\u00e0 Modric s\u1eafp t\u1edbi ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o s\u1ebd l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. H\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Croatia \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y nh\u1edd s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a hai ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang l\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe v\u00e0 Antoine Griezmann. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Giroud d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Deschamps nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Thomas Lemar, Nabir Fekir, Ousmane Dembele, Kimpembe v\u00e0 Tolisso, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Les Bleus. V\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Ph\u00e1p h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Croatia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u2018b\u1ecb b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t\u2019 khi \u0111ang c\u00f3 Mario Mandzukic - ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Croatia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o s\u1ecdc ca-r\u00f4 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Ante Rebic v\u00e0 Ivan Perisic, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ivan Rakitic s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m Modric, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t Marcelo Brozovic, Mateo Kovacic hay Ivan Perisic, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. N\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-croatia-21h-ngay-157-khi-tan-nhan-la-suc-manh-421-191227.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-croatia-21h-ngay-157-khi-tan-nhan-la-suc-manh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-croatia-21h-ngay-157-khi-tan-nhan-la-suc-manh-421-191227.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia (21h ng\u00e0y 15/7): Khi t\u00e0n nh\u1eabn l\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng t\u1edbi t\u00e0n nh\u1eabn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. L\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i cho th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Croatia<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u201cth\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng\u201d \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf Nam \u00c2u n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1i duy\u00ean \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o ca-r\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eafng n\u00e0y khi h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1eeda thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng.\u00a0<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"doi hinh Croatia tap luyen\" title=\"doi hinh Croatia tap luyen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/Hugo-Lloris-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Phap-vs-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng cho th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Croatia</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Boban, Suker hay Bilic c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 20 n\u0103m t\u1eebng tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hoa m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0a Croatia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Euro 1996 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Anh v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh h\u1ea1ng 3 t\u1ea1i c\u00fap b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf Ph\u00e1p n\u0103m 1998. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Modric v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed khi v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u2018l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng\u2019 Modric, Mandzukic, Ivan Perisic,\u2026. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, b\u00f9ng ch\u00e1y cho l\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i n\u00e0y r\u1ed3i \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean y\u00eau qu\u00fd c\u1ee7a Croatia \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a con c\u01b0ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>5. Griezmann li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 \u2018Vua v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec\u2019?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Antoine Griezmann, nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb trong l\u00e0ng t\u00fac c\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y ngo\u00e0i danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League v\u1eeba m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00ec Griezmann v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 duy\u00ean v\u1edbi c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann cua Phap\" title=\"Griezmann cua Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/griezmann-ngoa-ngoat-dap-tra-hazard-va-courtois-tuong-chelsea-cua-may-nguoi-la-barca-chac.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Griezmann \u0111ang r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2015/16 hay EURO 2016, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Griezmann \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea1m tay v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u danh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. N\u00f3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y s\u1edf h\u1eefu danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n cao qu\u00fd, Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, Griezmann s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia. 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n n\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n m\u00e0 anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i EURO hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Griezmann c\u1ea7n ch\u1eaft chiu t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u0103m 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-diem-mat-3-cap-doi-dau-dang-cho-doi-421-191119.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-diem-mat-3-cap-doi-dau-dang-cho-doi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-diem-mat-3-cap-doi-dau-dang-cho-doi-421-191119.html\">Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1eb7t 3 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang ta \u00edt gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 n\u1eefa. V\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e2u s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-phap-se-vo-dich-421-191099.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-phap-se-vo-dich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-phap-se-vo-dich-421-191099.html\">Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: 4 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0110T Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Croatia. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Deschamps s\u1ebd l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1270","checkdouble":"191245"},{"date":"08:09 15/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 17h00 ng\u00e0y 15/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/nhan-dinh-slna-vs-quang-nam-17h00-ngay-157-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>SLNA vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 15/7 (V\u00f2ng 19 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 17h00 ng\u00e0y 157 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 17h00 ng\u00e0y 157 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/SLNA-vs-Quang-Nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">SLNA vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span>SLNA vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam: 4-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>SLNA tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb t\u1ea1i V.League 2018. 1 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n n\u1eb1m \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng, khi\u1ebfn HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd h\u1ed3i sinh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. 6 v\u00f2ng v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecf t\u00fai s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a. Hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch Top 3 \u0111\u00fang 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, SLNA ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng ch\u1ea3y m\u00e1u l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o v\u00e0ng l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cua d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. M\u1ed9t khi nh\u1eefng V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc hay Tu\u1ea5n T\u00e0i\u2026 tr\u00fat b\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd th\u00ec h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, SLNA kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 3 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u00e0o h\u00e0ng ng\u0169 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng d\u00e0i nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed V.League. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, HAGL (2004) v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC (2018) \u0111ang c\u00f9ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu chu\u1ed7i 7 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, SLNA \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ch\u1ea3o l\u1eeda Vinh. Sau \u0111\u00f3 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua chu\u1ed7i 5 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn 4 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea1i 1-4 trong l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Vinh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 17 tr\u1eadn, SLNA th\u1eafng 7, h\u00f2a 5, thua 5.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a SLNA, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 5, h\u00f2a 2, thua 1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nSLNA: V\u0169 H\u1ea3i; Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u00ecnh Ho\u00e0ng, Th\u1ebf Nh\u1eadt, Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh, Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc, Xu\u00e2n Th\u1eafng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Lynch, Olaha.<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3ng Nam: V\u0103n C\u01b0\u1eddng; V\u0103n H\u1ecdc, Papel, V\u0103n H\u00e0, T\u1ea5n Sinh, Thanh Trung, H\u1eefu Ph\u01b0\u1edbc, Huy H\u00f9ng, V\u0103n Th\u1ea1nh, Quang Huy, Minh Tu\u1ea5n.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1269","checkdouble":"191223"},{"date":"08:16 15/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 17h00 ng\u00e0y 15/07 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/nhan-dinh-thanh-hoa-vs-quang-ninh-17h00-ngay-1507-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thanh H\u00f3a vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 15/07 (V\u00f2ng 19 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 17h00 ng\u00e0y 1507 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 17h00 ng\u00e0y 1507 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/thanh-hoa-vs-quang-ninh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Thanh H\u00f3a vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span>Thanh H\u00f3a vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: 1-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m SLNA, Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111ang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u0103ng ha. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, d\u00f9 b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n b\u00e3i, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 1-0. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 5 trong 6 v\u00f2ng v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 tr\u00ean BXH, \u00edt h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m (29 so v\u1edbi 31). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0,\u00a0FLC\u00a0Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 3 l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, ghi trung b\u00ecnh 2 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn. N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i, Thanh H\u00f3a m\u1edbi thua 1 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i t\u1ed5 \u1ea5m, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng 5, h\u00f2a 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3ng Ninh t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ee9ng ngay ph\u00eda sau \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Song, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 \u1edf 6 v\u00f2ng v\u1eeba qua. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i h\u1ecd m\u1edbi th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u00e0 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng. \u1ede chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t m\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 thua tr\u1eafng 4 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL. Ngo\u00e0i ra, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u00f2n cho th\u1ea5y, Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh ch\u01b0a m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n khi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Thanh H\u00f3a (h\u00f2a 1, thua 4).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 10 tr\u1eadn, Thanh H\u00f3a th\u1eafng 7, h\u00f2a 1, thua 2.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Thanh H\u00f3a, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 1, thua 0. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nThanh H\u00f3a: B\u1eedu Ng\u1ecdc, Xu\u00e2n Th\u00e0nh, Ti\u1ebfn Th\u00e0nh, V\u0103n Nam, Xu\u00e2n H\u01b0ng, Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng, H\u1eefu D\u0169ng, Ho\u00e0ng Th\u1ecbnh, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00f9ng, Gordon. <br>\r\nQu\u1ea3ng Ninh: Tu\u1ea5n Linh; Xu\u00e2n H\u00f9ng, V\u0103n Vi\u1ec7t, V\u0103n Tri\u1ec1u, Qu\u00e1ch T\u00e2n, H\u1ea3i Huy, Nguy\u00ean Sa, Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa, Kizito, Joel, Eydison.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1268","checkdouble":"191224"},{"date":"08:46 15/07","title":"HLV Roberto Martinez: \"Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/hlv-roberto-martinez-lukaku-da-co-mot-ky-world-cup-thanh-cong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Roberto Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Romelu Lukaku, c\u1ef1u HLV Everton kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o MU \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lukaku c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup 2018 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. Trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Panama v\u00e0 Tunisia \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roberto Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Romelu Lukaku h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Roberto Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Romelu Lukaku h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Roberto-Martinez-phat-bieu-ve-Romelu-Lukaku-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lukaku c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Lukaku \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o MU kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 3-2 nh\u01b0ng Lukaku kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Brazil, B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng song ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1993 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Lukaku l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1. T\u1ed1i qua, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-bi-vs-anh-463-191173.html\" target=\"_blank\">B\u1ec9 vs Anh </span>trong tr\u1eadn tranh gi\u1ea3i 3, Lukaku ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c im ti\u1ebfng, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t may l\u00e0 B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLukaku \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i trong 4 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018, anh \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga v\u1edbi 4 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Roberto Martinez khen ng\u1ee3i Lukaku</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roberto Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Romelu Lukaku, c\u1ef1u HLV Everton kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o MU \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lukaku\" title=\"Lukaku\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/hlv-roberto-martinez-lukaku-da-co-mot-ky-world-cup-thanh-cong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV B\u1ec9 khen ng\u1ee3i Lukaku</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Romelu, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c anh \u1ea5y di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c an \u1ee7i ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh gi\u1ea3i 3. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1267","checkdouble":"191225"},{"date":"08:43 15/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia (21h ng\u00e0y 15/7): Khi t\u00e0n nh\u1eabn l\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/15/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-croatia-21h-ngay-157-khi-tan-nhan-la-suc-manh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng t\u1edbi t\u00e0n nh\u1eabn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang nh\u01b0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch FIFA, Gianni Infantino \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y: World Cup 2018 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc g\u00e2y h\u1ed3i h\u1ed9p \u0111\u1ebfn ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u1ed1c x\u1ea3y ra r\u1ed3i c\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac m\u1edbi l\u1ea1 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd video VAR.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau c\u00f9ng, Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Croatia l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. V\u1edbi ri\u00eang ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ai ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ee9c, T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Argentina r\u1ed3i Brazil kh\u00f4ng \u0111i qu\u00e1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Didier Deschamps bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 21h ng\u00e0y 157 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 21h ng\u00e0y 157 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-croatia-21h-ngay-157-khi-tan-nhan-la-suc-manh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft 21h ng\u00e0y 15/7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t. Tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann g\u00e2y khi\u1ebfp s\u1ee3 cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 khi c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Olivier Giroud h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho h\u1ecd. \u1ede ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u0169i c\u00f4ng l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Fekir, Dembele, Lemar hay Thauvin\u2026<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n sau 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi 3 l\u00e0 t\u1edbi trong m\u00e0n r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina (th\u1eafng 4-3). So v\u1edbi 4 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 B\u1ec9, Anh hay Croatia, Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phap thang Bi 1-0\" title=\"Phap thang Bi 1-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Deschamps-phat-bieu-sau-tran-dau-Phap-1-0-Bi-ban-ket-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ph\u00e1p th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay t\u1eeb trung tuy\u1ebfn, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng Pogba hay Kante c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. C\u1ea3 ba \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu ngu\u1ed3n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 v\u00f4 t\u1eadn, lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 c\u1eb7p Varane v\u00e0 Umtiti \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Pique v\u00e0 Ramos c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha. N\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i tr\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Les Bleus c\u0169ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Hugo Lloris r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 minh h\u1ecda cho s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec r\u00f5 n\u00e9t h\u01a1n b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. \u0110\u1ebfn Brazil ch\u1ec9 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n sau 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u c\u0169ng 2 l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Nh\u01b0ng Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Hazard c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n im ti\u1ebfng. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phap vs Bi Kante tranh bong voi De Bruyne\" title=\"Phap vs Bi Kante tranh bong voi De Bruyne\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/Phap-vs-Bi-Kante-tranh-bong-voi-De-Bruyne.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Les Bleus c\u1ee7a Kante c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 HLV Deschamps (xu\u1ea5t th\u00e2n t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1) r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi trong chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t. Khi ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 h\u1ecfa l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc. Nh\u01b0ng khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef g\u00ecn th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, \u1edf Ph\u00e1p lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e0n nh\u1eabn. Khi \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf qu\u00e2n b\u00ecnh v\u00e0 sau c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/umtiti-phap-khong-duoc-phep-quen-chung-ket-euro-2016-421-191148.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/umtiti-phap-khong-duoc-phep-quen-chung-ket-euro-2016.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/umtiti-phap-khong-duoc-phep-quen-chung-ket-euro-2016-421-191148.html\">Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p qu\u00ean chung k\u1ebft EURO 2016</span><br>\r\n<span>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00ean nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft EURO 2016.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nCroatia c\u00f3 t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng l\u1ef1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y Croatia hi\u1ec7n nay c\u00f2n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi \u201cth\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng\u201d c\u1ee7a Davor Suker \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup n\u0103m 1998. \u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Luka Modric c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Anh h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng Rakitic v\u00e0 Brozovic th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Perisic v\u00e0 Rebic v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1edbt s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. C\u00f2n \u1edf trung t\u00e2m, Croatia c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Mandzukic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dejan Lovren cung dang tai tam anh tap the DT Croatia an mung chien thang.\" title=\"Dejan Lovren c\u0169ng \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0110T Croatia \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Ivan-Perisic-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Phap-vs-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Croatia khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00ecn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh v\u1edbi th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia d\u00f9 nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u00fd ch\u00ed v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng khoa h\u1ecdc c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n. N\u1ebfu Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n l\u1ef1c khi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Croatia m\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Croatia c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i \u00f4m h\u1eadn. May m\u1eafn l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o caro kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef n\u00e0o t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t. C\u00f3 Strinic v\u00e0 Mandzukic b\u1ecb \u0111au nh\u1eb9 song nh\u00ecn chung v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Luzhniki.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"doi hinh Croatia tap luyen\" title=\"doi hinh Croatia tap luyen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/doi-hinh-Croatia-tap-luyen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, Strinic v\u00e0 Mandzukic hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a Croatia c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 3 v\u00f2ng bao g\u1ed3m 1/8 v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Nga hay b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Anh, The Blazers \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQua \u0111\u00f3, Croatia s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ng\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn. \u1ede b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Anh, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Modric hay Rakitic c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. \u0110\u00e3 th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ngh\u1ec9 \u00edt h\u01a1n 1 ng\u00e0y so v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c Phi v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 sung m\u00e3n v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ebd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho t\u1edbi t\u1eadn ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t c\u1ee7a Croatia. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi c\u00f3 t\u00e2m m\u00e0 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p nung n\u1ea5u gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup sau 20 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p (4-3-3): </strong>1.Lloris - 2.Pavard, 5.Umtiti, 4.Varane, 21.Hern\u00e1ndez - 14.Matuidi, 13.Kant\u00e9, 6.Pogba - 10.Mbapp\u00e9, 9.Giroud, 7.Griezmann<br>\r\n<strong>Croatia (4-1-4-1):</strong> 23.Subasic - 2.Vrsaljko, 6.Lovren, 21.Vida, 3.Strinic - 11.Brozovic - 18.Rebic, 10.Modric, 7.Rakitic, 4.Perisic - 17.Mandzukic<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1:</strong> Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng 1-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Phap vs Croatia\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/Phap-vs-Croatia-(4-3-1-2-vs-4-1-4-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-doat-qua-bong-vang-ngay-nam-nay-tai-sao-khong-421-191211.html\">Mbappe \u0111o\u1ea1t Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng ngay n\u0103m nay, t\u1ea1i sao kh\u00f4ng?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-ngoa-ngoat-dap-tra-hazard-va-courtois-tuong-chelsea-cua-may-nguoi-la-barca-chac-421-191190.html\">Griezmann ngoa ngo\u1eaft \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois: T\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea c\u1ee7a m\u1ea5y ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0 Barca ch\u1eafc?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/choang-voi-ly-do-tien-dao-griezmann-ghi-it-ban-thang-tai-world-cup-2018-421-191188.html\">Cho\u00e1ng v\u1edbi l\u00fd do ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Griezmann ghi \u00edt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/olivier-giroud-sat-thu-dac-biet-389-191174.html\">Olivier Giroud: S\u00e1t th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/an-tuong-world-cup/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-phap-tim-lai-anh-hao-quang-nam-xua-471-191128.html\">B\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup: Ph\u00e1p t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i \u00e1nh h\u00e0o quang n\u0103m x\u01b0a</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1266","checkdouble":"191227"},{"date":"04:06 15/07","title":"HLV Roberto Martinez: \"Quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/hlv-roberto-martinez-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-dt-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Roberto Martinez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi \"th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng\" l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 ba t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-191191.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/211837-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-191191.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 2-0 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nMeunier v\u00e0 Hazard gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh trong tr\u1eadn tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba v\u1edbi Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-0. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u1ec9 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i World Cup. N\u0103m 1986, &quot;qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&quot; ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Roberto Martinez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Roberto Martinez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/hlv-roberto-martinez-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-dt-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Roberto Martinez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Roberto Martinez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ra t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng. Khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil v\u00e0 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng. L\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 1986<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Roberto Martinez cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 1986 l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u1ec9. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 t\u1ea1i Mexico 86 l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u1ec9&quot; - HLV Roberto Martinez ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: &quot;Gi\u1edd th\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. M\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn 32 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y n\u00ean d\u0129 nhi\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i mang ch\u1ea5t B\u1ec9, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u. Ch\u1ea5t k\u1ebft d\u00ednh v\u00e0 linh ho\u1ea1t m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c gia&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba, World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i l\u00e0 chung k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 22h00 ng\u00e0y 15/7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-giup-bi-danh-bai-dt-anh-de-dang-466-191208.html\">3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-chien-thang-lich-su-cua-dt-bi-truoc-anh-469-191205.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\">N\u00f3ng: Hazard \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nothing-is-coming-home-dau-la-ly-do-khien-dt-anh-trang-tay-tai-world-cup-2018-421-191202.html\">Nothing is coming home: \u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Anh tr\u1eafng tay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/roy-keane-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-dt-anh-421-191201.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-southgate-noi-ve-tran-thua-cua-dt-anh-465-191200.html\">HLV Southgate n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh: Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3o t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1265","checkdouble":"191209"}]}